 A smalle shuttle fell from the sky. This old warrior locked down his ship as 
it crashed into a pile of raw energon. His beast scanner came out and only 
found raw energon signatures. The sound voiced. "Too much energon error.  A 
skeleton of a bot came out. Its eyes red. Suddenly a white cloud of pure 
energy surronded him. His hands extended forwards he looked at himself. "I am 
Archon....I am energy." He floated across the grassy field. His ship blew up 
behind him. he sent a com to the Maximal city near by. "I am Archon Maximal 
warrior please respond."

--part1_d.1914b4c0.28aad188_boundary
